 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20071212051548/http://www.armchairempire.com/Reviews/PC%20Games/freelancer.htm
 |archivedate = 2007-12-12
}}
</ref>。多人模式的背景设定与单人游戏相同，但不会发生单人游戏的剧情<ref name="gntv">{{cite web
 |author=Kristopher Abel 
 |title=Freelancer Review 
 |publisher=Game Nation TV 
