 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070821223731/http://www.gamenationtv.com/reviews/freelancer.shtml 
 |archivedate=2007-08-21 
}}
</ref>。一台[[个人电脑|个人电脑]]可以担当容纳128名玩家进行连线的[[服务器|服务器]]<ref>{{cite web
 |author      = Christian "Catachan" D'Amico
